rows.label: qst700504_msg0001
rows.name:
It's ready? Thanks, you've done
a fantastic job.

rows.label: qst700504_msg0002
rows.name:
Listen, could you stick around for
a moment?

rows.label: qst700504_msg0003
rows.name:
I was hoping I could introduce you
to my client before you go. I saw him
near the palace gardens just now.

rows.label: qst700504_msg0004
rows.name:
Besides, after all the hard work you
put in, I could hardly tell him I made it,
could I? Go on, it won't take a second.

rows.label: qst700504_msg0005
rows.name:
And no, before you start getting any
ideas, I am not too embarrassed to
give it to him in person.

rows.label: qst700504_msg0006
rows.name:
Sachsum Gardens, all right?
Got that? Good. And don't you dare
run out on me!
